<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-78-0264 </DOCNO><TEXT>Implementation of the radiological information system SIMEDOS in the centraldepartment of diagnostic radiology in the Marburg University Hospitalis discussed. Special attention is given to the clinical and organizationalproblems of the department, as well as the planning and preparation phasesof system implementation. This system has been in use for 10 months andour experience concerning problem-solving and the various user groupsis described.</TEXT></DOC>